The difficulty in gathering data:

One of the special challenges in building this platform was the scarcity of easily accessible datasets related to EdTech competencies and business requirements. In order to get above this obstacle, we manually gathered information from the LinkedIn site, guaranteeing the precision and applicability of our suggestions.
